 Airborne Division|82nd Airborne (ABN) Div]]</center>\nFile:504th Infantry Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div's 1st IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-501st PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN Div, 1st IBCT's 501st Inf Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:504InfRegt1BnFlash.PNG|<center>82nd ABN Div, 1st IBCT's [[504th Infantry Regiment (United States)|504th Inf Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:504InfRegt2BnFlash.png|<center>82nd ABN Div, 1st IBCT's 504th Inf Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army-82nd Airborne Division-2nd Brigade Combat Team-Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div's 2nd IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-325th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div, 2nd IBCT's [[325th Infantry Regiment (United States)|325th Inf Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-325th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div, 2nd IBCT's 325th Inf Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-508th PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN Div, 2nd IBCT's [[508th Infantry Regiment (United States)|508th Inf Regiment]], 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army-82nd Airborne Division-3rd Brigade Combat Team-Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div's 3rd IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-505th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div, 3rd IBCT's [[505th Infantry Regiment (United States)|505th Inf Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-505th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div, 3rd IBCT's 505th Inf Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-508th PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN Div, 3rd IBCT's 508th Inf Regiment, 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 173rd ABN INF BCT Flash.png|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd ABN Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 143rd ABN INF BN Flash.png|<center>173rd ABN Brigade's [[143rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|143rd Inf Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd ABN Brigade's [[503rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|503rd Inf Regim