on 3)}}\n{{:The Amazing World of Gumball (season 3)}}\n\n===Season 4 (2015\u201316)===\n{{main|The Amazing World of Gumball (season 4)}}\n{{:The Amazing World of Gumball (season 4)}}\n\n===Season 5 (2016\u201317)===\n{{main|The Amazing World of Gumball (season 5)}}\n{{:The Amazing World of Gumball (season 5)}}\n\n===Season 6 (2018\u201319)===\n{{main|The Amazing World of Gumball (season 6)}}\n{{:The Amazing World of Gumball (season 6)}}\n\n==''Darwin's Yearbook'' (2019-2020)==\nA six-episode special called ''Darwin's Yearbook'' aired on Cartoon Network in December 2019. The miniseries features Darwin attempting to complete Elmore Junior High's yearbook by examining who he thinks should fill up the best spot. The miniseries is essentially a collection of [[clip show]] episodes.<ref name=anim>{{cite web|url=https://www.animationmagazine.net/tv/cn-brings-back-gumball-with-special-darwins-yearbook-episodes/|title=CN Brings Back 'Gumball' with Special \"Darwin's Yearbook\" Episodes|website=Animation Magazine|last=Milligan|first=Mercedes|date=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:100%;margin:auto;\"\n|- style=\"color:white\"\n! style=\"background:#F28500;color:black;\" width=5%|No. in<br />series\n! style=\"background:#F28500;color:black;\" width=12%|Title\n! style=\"background:#F28500;color:black;\" width=13%|U.S. air date\n! style=\"background:#F28500;color:black;\" width=10%|U.K. air date\n! style=\"background:#F28500;color:black;\" width=1%|Prod.<br />code\n! style=\"background:#F28500;color:black;\" width=1%|U.S. viewers<br />(millions)\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=1\n|Title=Banana Joe\n| RTitle={{Efn|name=yearbook1|This episode was first aired in France on December 7, 2019.}}\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2019|12|14}}\n|AltDate=December 2, 2019<ref>{{cite tweet|user=RegularTweetsUK|number=1191671077052862464|date=November 5, 2019|title=Thread: Official Confirmation from Cartoon Network UK: BRAND NEW: THE AMAZING WORLD OF G